    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and runs like a dream. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and enjoy the drive. Come check it out and take it for a spin; I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
