    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been looked after with a lot of care over the years. It drives smoothly and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, comfy ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve had some great memories in this car, and I\u2019m excited for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have! Come check it out!",
