    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six masterpiece. The power unit features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, delivering visceral induction noise and linear power delivery. It is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and reliability. The chassis is sorted with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the precise steering rack feedback and lateral composure these cars are known for. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain integrity remain excellent.",
